page0.title: Play Word Nerd
page0.content: | Word Nerd | . Word Nerd . Word Nerd . </html> . How to Play How to Play . Guess the word in 6 tries. . Each guess must be a valid 5-letter word. . The color of the squares will change to show how close your guess was to the word. . Green - Letter is in the word and in the correct spot. . Yellow - Letter is in the word but in the wrong spot. . Grey - Letter is not in the word in any spot. . Close Settings Settings . Sound . Sound Language . Español English . Close q w e r t y u i o p Del a s d f g h j k l Enter z x c v b n m

page1.title: About
page1.content: Hi! We are Aliya, Ananya, Claire, and Sreeja from Mr.Yeung’s 5th period class. We made “Word Nerd”, a game similar to Wordle for our project. .
